1002500.1000851.1000867.group=Exterior 1002500.1000851.1000867.description=The key here is containment – this bed net helps secure your tools and gear:
•Accommodates various shapes and sizes to contain cargo during normal driving conditions
•Durable nylon netting is stain resistant so it maintains a "like-new" appearance
•Easily attaches to the truck bed
•Folds flat when not in use
